Package io.sentry

Interface BackfillingEventProcessor

All Superinterfaces:
EventProcessor
public interface BackfillingEventProcessor extends EventProcessor
Marker interface for event processors that process events that have to be backfilled, i.e. currently stored in-memory data (like Scope or SentryOptions) is irrelevant, because the event happened in the past.
